      <body>This looks like a regression.

Before 2.3:

    /               =&gt;  public/index.html
    /foo/bar/  =&gt;  public/foo/bar/index.html

After 2.3:

    /              =&gt;  public/index.html
    /foo/bar/ =&gt;  404</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This looks like a regression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before 2.3:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code&gt;/               =&amp;gt;  public/index.html
/foo/bar/  =&amp;gt;  public/foo/bar/index.html
&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After 2.3:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&lt;code&gt;/              =&amp;gt;  public/index.html
/foo/bar/ =&amp;gt;  404
&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
